title: Show ascii value for most keys
message:
Show ascii value for most keys

We need to have the keymap looking like the other keymaps in AOSP; show
the characters that are printable ASCII as-is, and not as uniode.

We update the generator to do that.

title: Update key character map
message:
Update key character map

We update the generation script to be able to use the 102ND key, and
remap all keys to QWERTY layout in order to use the BÉPO character map
consistently, even on AZERTY and other keyboards.

The generated file now has a license, and it's the same as this
project's.

title: Update generator and generated file
